Fetch Pull Only changes are copied into your local Git repository and does not reflect the changes It copies changes from a remote repository directly into your working directory and reflect the changes. Fetch just fetch pull = fetch + merge <pre><code># one way
git fetch origin &lt;branch-name&gt;
git merge origin/&lt;branch-name&gt;

# another way
git pull origin &lt;branch-name&gt; # or just git pull
</code></pre>
